data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath home on one of the best lots in the addition.  Spacious corner lot with nice fenced back yard the owners had installed after purchasing. The barreled ceiling entry leads to a large living room that has a cozy fireplace ad open concept into the kitchen for plenty of space for entertaining family and friends.  The kitchen consists of beautiful custom built cabinetry with a large island and quartz counter top.  Master bedroom ensuite features a doorless walk-in tiled shower and a separate garden tub.  Master closet also connects to the utility room for convenience.  Come take a look at this beauty today!
